Scott Allen DOORNINK, Applicant-Appellant,
v.
STATE of Iowa, Respondent-Appellee. No. 18-0429 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed May 1, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

Scott Doornink appeals the district court's denial of his application for postconviction relief. AFFIRMED.

AFFIRMED.
